data.title: F-WWSK . Airbus A380-841 . Airbus Industries . Paris - Le Bourget [LBG/LFPB]
data.meta_description:
Be sure that the photo is noting compared to see this approach with your own eyes !!! Airbus sent this A380 for the 'Salon international de l'aéronautique et de l'espace de Paris 2013' which is seen here performing it's final adjustments on VPT Runway 25. 
	Now part of British Airways fleet as G-XLEA.
	© Erwan Pambrun-Vincent - Tous droits réservés
